# Documentation issues 

This is a planning document to address issues about developing guidance documents for scientific software hackathons. 

## Issues 

* scoping questions 
* audience 
* which kinds of materials?  what formats?  
    * a main "how to" that will be published 
    * supporting materials 
        * sample announcement
        * sample application form 
        * sample review form
        * sample budget 
        * tip sheet for guiding team-formation
* how will they be accessed? 
* how will we reach the audience 
